pamir-ai-eink-dkms (1.0.0-2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Major refactoring: Split monolithic driver into multiple files
  * Added comprehensive update mode support (full, partial, base map)
  * Implemented proper mmap support using vmalloc_user
  * Added IOCTL interface for advanced control
  * Added sysfs interface for runtime configuration
  * Fixed all kernel coding style issues
  * Added deep sleep mode support
  * Improved error handling and recovery
  * Added comprehensive documentation and examples

 -- Pamir AI <support@pamir.ai>  Thu, 28 Aug 2025 01:09:58 +0530

